title: 296. Andy & DJ CTI: Chinese Military Audio Leaked, Trump-Russia Trial Opens & Kim Jong Un Lookalike
itunes:title: 296. Andy & DJ CTI: Chinese Military Audio Leaked, Trump-Russia Trial Opens & Kim Jong Un Lookalike
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the exclusive audio leak of the Chinese Military meeting discussing the invasion of Taiwan, the trial opening in the Trump-Russia case of Hillary Clinton's 'Alfa Bank' lawyer, and a Kim Jong Un lookalike disrupting an Australian election campaign.
